OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome late sunshine this evening but
OL,7,Fdull along the east coast. The rest of
OL,8,Fthe night will be dry with variable
OL,9,Famounts of cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FIt will be dry with a fair
OL,12,Famount of cloud across the west. Some
OL,13,Fsunshine breaking through across the
OL,14,Feast. Breezy. Warm in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,17,FOutbreaks of rain will spread east on
OL,18,FSaturday, occasionally heavy later.
OL,19,FScattered showers on Sunday. Further
OL,20,Frain likely on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
